  <p>Certain portions of the website request that you provide personally identifiable information, to FanClash in order to register for services, create an account, or request additional information or literature. If you provide us with personally identifiable information for these purposes, we may provide that information to third-parties, subject to applicable law. If you do not wish to have your information shared with these third-parties then please do not provide us with that information.</p>

  <p>FanClash may also disclose personally identifiable information in order to respond to a subpoena, court order or other such request. FanClash may also provide such personally identifiable information in response to a law enforcement agency's request or as otherwise required by law.</p>

  <p>Your personally identifiable information may be provided to a third party if FanClash files for bankruptcy, or there is a transfer of the assets or ownership of FanClash in connection with proposed or consummated corporate reorganizations, such as mergers or acquisitions.</p><br />

